My names Claret, though people just call me Charetta usually... why do they bother calling me such things if it means so much to them anyway right?! But aside from that.. i'm an ordinary office worker now; everyone does what comes natural after all~

You are very handsome… am not saying anything more flirtatious than this honestly because there’re plenty others which would probably say exactly opposite thing while being way less attractive 😉 idk tho maybe one day we will become romantic heheh~. Anyway glad tto meet you ~"
